{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds a shadow to this view."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"shadow"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"color"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Color","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore5ColorV"},{"kind":"text","text":" = Color(.sRGBLinear, white: 0, opacity: 0.33), "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"radius"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CGFloat","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"x"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CGFloat","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV"},{"kind":"text","text":" = 0, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"y"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CGFloat","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV"},{"kind":"text","text":" = 0) -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"color","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The shadow’s color.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"radius","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A measure of how much to blur the shadow. Larger values","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"result in more blur.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"x","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An amount to offset the shadow horizontally from the view."}]}]},{"name":"y","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An amount to offset the shadow vertically from the view."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that adds a shadow to this view."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier to add a shadow of a specified color behind a view."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You can offset the shadow from its view independently in the horizontal"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and vertical dimensions using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"x"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"y"},{"type":"text","text":" parameters. You can also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"blur the edges of the shadow using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"radius"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter. Use a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"radius of zero to create a sharp shadow. Larger radius values produce"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"softer shadows."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The example below creates a grid of boxes with varying offsets and blur."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Each box displays its radius and offset values for reference."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["struct Shadow: View {","    let steps = [0, 5, 10]","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            ForEach(steps, id: \\.self) { offset in","                HStack(spacing: 50) {","                    ForEach(steps, id: \\.self) { radius in","                        Color.blue","                            .shadow(","                                color: .primary,","                                radius: CGFloat(radius),","                                x: CGFloat(offset), y: CGFloat(offset))","                            .overlay {","                                VStack {","                                    Text(\"\\(radius)\")","                                    Text(\"(\\(offset), \\(offset))\")","                                }","                            }","                    }","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The example above uses "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color\/primary","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" as the color to make the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shadow easy to see for the purpose of illustration. In practice,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you might prefer something more subtle, like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Color\/gray-8j2b"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you don’t specify a color, the method uses a semi-transparent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"black."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ForEach"]]},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE6shadow5color6radius1x1yQrAA5ColorV_14CoreFoundation7CGFloatVA2MtF::SYNTHESIZED::s:15OpenSwiftUICore7ForEachV","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"shadow"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"color"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifi